Group Dining
Thank you for your interest in hosting your event at Tampa’s premier rooftop destination! Perched high above historic Armature Works, our luxurious, deco-inspired lounge and restaurant offers unparalleled waterfront views of Tampa. We offer a variety of spaces for your social gathering, along with carefully curated food and drink packages.
